ibility, so this points to the need for\na hybrid simulation approach where efficient simulations of much larger number\nof solvent molecules is carried out using a lower level of theory while\nretaining the higher level of theory for the reacting molecules as well as\ntheir near neighbors and the catalyst.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2023 17:16:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-06"}
